WEBVTT

00:02:59.200 --> 00:03:01.616
Wiki kadhaa baadae nilikua nyumbani
kwa rafiki yangu,

00:03:01.640 --> 00:03:07.560
na nilikua nimesikitika kweli na hasira kuhusu
chuki zote na ubaguzi wa rangi nliokutana nao.

00:03:08.840 --> 00:03:11.856
Ilikua ni yeye aliependekeza
natakiwa niwapigie

00:03:11.880 --> 00:03:13.080
na niwatembelee.

00:03:14.680 --> 00:03:16.120
"Wataniua," nilisema.

00:03:17.560 --> 00:03:21.096
"Hawawezi kushambulia mshiriki
wa bunge la Denmark," alisema.

00:03:21.120 --> 00:03:25.136
"Na hata hivyo, kama wakikuua,
utakua shahidi."

00:03:25.160 --> 00:03:27.296
(Kicheko)

00:03:27.320 --> 00:03:29.896
"Hivyo kwako utakua umeshinda pande zote."

00:03:29.920 --> 00:03:32.160
(Kicheko)